name: dHealth
description: dHealth - The Framework For Health-to-Earn dHealth Network offers plug-and-play components and shared blockchain infrastructure to execute global healthcare use-cases and payment systems seamlessly. DHP (Digital Health Points) is the native token of the dHealth Network. DHP are cross-chain compatible and power the global dHealth ecosystem. Currently, DHP are available as native DHP on dHealth Network and as ERC20 DHP on Ethereum.
